{"tid":1776592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"先係槍放蛇，今晚就屈放炸彈，港共又想屈恐怖主義","createTime":"2019-12-09T15:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T16:16:41.000Z","uid":188176,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a81a26fb62ad85a75c5be497896541cf026b1524","tid":1776592,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:52:17.000Z","msg":"好心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到今時今日仲想屈恐怖主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界都睇穿你手腳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想用恐怖主義屈抗爭者<br />\n愈係咁做，只會比全世界睇清楚你唔再係警察<br />\n幾個月前美國個邊仲話同香港警察合作無間只係中共問題<br />\n到今日特登整條act出黎制裁香港警察<br />\n而家國際包圍網形成緊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警犬你班國際恐怖分子等國際制裁</span>"},{"pid":"0ff99744edd2702424b19eee628c423c6eca359a","tid":1776592,"uid":31699,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"第一次出現紙皮箱就出拆彈機械人<br />\n今次就唔洗引爆 班popo直接拎上手影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW即然真槍炸彈都已出現<br />\n夠料出宵禁令未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6748816bf511c46a6dbcbe72fad36deaf491211","tid":1776592,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:57:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c813f1facf544c6fd8181fa12911ad4a018800c","tid":1776592,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"921d399dc36071abae1a1355381696c1cccd31a1","tid":1776592,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ff997